{
  "stem": "617.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then there was room to walk around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As we came in the door, we would go onto that walk and then climb over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Which wasn't much of a climbing, but you know, just something to keep the straw from the center.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We would just go onto our beds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we would sit there and-- and lice out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And clean the lice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And after a while, you know, less and less people, we were less and less.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we would already hear the shooting, you know, like from far, like, far from distance.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we knew there was something going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then one day, we got up, and we were told that they're moving out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was in January, 1945.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That we were moving out of this camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the oberscharfuhrer, who was our [INAUDIBLE] officer said, that they will have-- we will be marching, and we will be sort of about five or so in a line and marching.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the sick, he said, will go with us, but they will be taken on a-- in a cart, which it was so, yes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were put on a cart and taken.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But two of the-- there were three sisters together, and one of them was sick.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she was in the infirmary.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they didn't believe that the sick ones will come with us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So the two sisters asked to get her sister out from the infirmary, and she will be able to walk.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Of course, she didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She was very weak.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the two sisters, like, they would hold her, one on one side, one on the other side.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
